                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "If someone of ill intent seeks to enter Aaru Village, the only thing that will greet them will be the pointed spears of the guards. The dutiful guard, Fodil, had faced plenty of powerful foes in his youth, and thus possessed a deep well of experience to draw from, with some of his new foes breathing clarity into old memories...",
